Inverted Pyramid
description:
La Pyramide Inversée (The Inverted Pyramid) is a skylight constructed in an underground shopping mall in front of the Louvre Museum in France.

In "The Da Vinci Code" (novel and film) the pyramid is said to shelter the Holy Grail.
